      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exemplary caliber, maintained to an uncompromising showroom standard. This specimen exhibits flawless aesthetic and mechanical integrity, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Every detail reflects a pedigree of meticulous stewardship, ensuring an experience indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 44900.0,
